name: HY-PHEN-AT-ED
description: HY-PHEN-AT-ED, would have been an imaginary band had they ever banded. This incredible Neo-Krautrock duo hail from the not-so-distant future in Lagos, Nigeria. After most nations on the continent became industrialized, there was a deep nostalgic movement of young people that wanted to hark back to a simpler time in music. Their sound, directly influenced by Dusseldorf's great-great-great grandfathers of electronic music, Kraftwerk. This is the music of 2077, an incredible combination of African instruments with the minimalistic execution of 70s Krautrock.
